{"lemma":"وَجْهَيْ","slug":"وَجْهَيْ","root":"#.ج.ه","root_slug":"_-ج-ه","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ج-ه","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"وَجْه","root":"وجه","pos":"N","occurrence_count":72},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":18},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n44469"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D9%87%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be a man of distinction, to be notable"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to raise to eminence, to distinguish, to honor"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to turn one’s face, to turn","examples":[{"text":"وَجَّهَ وَجْهَهُ/ظَهْرَهُ إِلَى شَخْصٍ","english":"to turn one's face to/back on someone"},{"text":"وَجَّهَ خُطَاهُ نَحْوَ شَيْءٍ","english":"to turn one's steps to(wards) something"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to head for"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to send, to dispatch","examples":[{"text":"وَجَّهَ رِسَالَةً/طَلَبًا إِلَى شَخْصٍ","english":"to send a letter/request to someone"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to aim, to direct, to steer","examples":[{"text":"وَجَّهَ مُسَدَّسًا إِلَى شَخْصٍ","english":"to aim a pistol at someone"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to guide"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to address","examples":[{"text":"وَجَّهَ الكَلَامَ/الخِطَابَ إِلَى شَخْصٍ","english":"to address someone"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bring a charge against"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"utter","examples":[{"text":"وَجَّهَ تَحْذِيرَاتٍ إِلَى شَخْصٍ","english":"to warn someone"},{"text":"وَجَّهَ تُهْمَةً إِلَى شَخْصٍ","english":"to accuse someone"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"essence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"face"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"face, countenance"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"front, façade"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"watch dial"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"outside, exterior, surface"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"method, manner, mode, fashion, wise"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"aspect, perspective","examples":[{"text":"أَبْشِرِي فَإِنَّكِ تَلِدِينَ غُلَامًا إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّٰهُ تَعَالَى فَأُسَمِّيهِ ٱسْمًا حَسَنًا ثُمَّ أُؤَدِّبُهُ أَحْسَنَ ٱلْأَدَبِ وَأُعَلِّمُهُ وُجُوهَ ٱلْعِلْمِ فَيَكُونَ لَنَا عُقْبًا صَالِحًا وَأَنَا مُتَقَدِّمٌ فِي ٱلْتِمَاسِ ٱلْأَظْآرِ لَهُ.","english":"Rejoice, for you’re going to give birth to a boy, God willing. I’ll choose a beautiful name, give him the finest upbringing, and teach him all sorts of subjects, and we shall have a righteous legacy. I’ll set out at once to find nurses for him."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/wa.d͡ʒu.ha/","/wad͡ʒh/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44469","headword_ar":"وَجْهٌ","root":"wjh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asolamotu wajohiY ll~`h","text_ar":"اَسْلَمْتُ وَجْهِى للّٰه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I resigned, or resign, myself to God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I became, or become, *"},{"kind":"page_break","n":3050},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Muslim:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wjh","text_ar":"وجه"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here used for the whole because it is the most noble part: (Jel, ii. 106:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*AtY","text_ar":"ذاتى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"my course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino kul~i wajohK","text_ar":"مِنْ كُلِّ وَجْهٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In every respect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"considered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from every point of view."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwajohu A^ano yakuwna ka*aA","text_ar":"الوَجْهُ اَنْ يَكُونَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proper"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reasonable"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way is that it should be thus:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the valid and obvious"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turoEapN","text_ar":"تُرْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A course, a purpose, or an object,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which one is pursuing;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a direction"},{"kind":"text","text":"in which one is going or looking, & c. as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihapN","text_ar":"جِهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing. (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa","text_ar":"لَيْسَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"likalAamika wajohN","text_ar":"لِكَلاَمِكَ وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no truth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or correctness,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in thy saying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Brightness"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of intellect]. (L, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liwajohi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"لِوَجْهِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kur, lxxvi. 9)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"For the sake of God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to obtain the countenance"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favour of God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull, p. 378.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY *aAti A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"فِى ذَاتِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw","text_ar":"ذُو"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawokaAna ka*aA lakaAna wajohFA","text_ar":"لَوْكَانَ كَذَا لَكَانَ وَجْهًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Were it so, it were reasonable."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA wajoha lahu","text_ar":"لَا وَجْهَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a phrase, &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no reasonable way of accounting for it."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laysa biAlwajohi","text_ar":"لَيسَ بِالوَجْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa","text_ar":"لَيْسَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biwajiypK","text_ar":"بِوَجِيةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Not of respectable, or esteemed, or high, authority:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(said of a word or phrase, &c.:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is not the proper way."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AibotigaA'a wajohi All~`hi","text_ar":"اِبْتِغَاءَ وَجْهِ اللّٰهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"From a desire of God's recompense:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kur, ii. 274; and Expos. of the Jeláleyn:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"countenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favour."},{"kind":"text","text":"There are several similar phrases in the Kur, where"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wjh","text_ar":"وجه"},{"kind":"text","text":"is explained in the same sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawaAbN","text_ar":"ثَوَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Expos. of the Jeláleyn. ―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabasahu Eano wajohihi","text_ar":"جَبَسَهُ عَنْ وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He withheld him, or restrained him, from his course, purpose, or object"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt","text_ar":"الت"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sarafa Al$~aYo'a Eano wajohuhu","text_ar":"صَرَفَ الشَّىْءَ عَنْ وَجْهُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He turned the thing away, or back, from its"},{"kind":"text","text":"course,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano sananihi","text_ar":"عَنْ سَنَنِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b16-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraja wajohuhu","text_ar":"خَرَجَ وَجْهُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mrd","text_ar":"مرد"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and L voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstElj","text_ar":"استعلج"},{"kind":"text","text":";) [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraja","text_ar":"خَرَجَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabaAtu wajohihi","text_ar":"نَبَاتُ وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hair of his face grew forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b17-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohu Ald~ahori","text_ar":"وَجْهُ الدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beginning of time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahaArK","text_ar":"نَهَارٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b18-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAhu EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"رَوَاهُ عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qS","text_ar":"قص"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~ava bihi EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"حَدَّثَ بِهِ عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qS","text_ar":"قص"},{"kind":"text","text":":) see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~a","text_ar":"قَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b19-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotu AlA^amora","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُ الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino wajahihi","text_ar":"مِنْ وَجَهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c., and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihatihi","text_ar":"جِهَتِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA^otFY","text_ar":"مَاْتًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b20-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drift"},{"kind":"text","text":"of speech. (K, Kull, p. 378.) ―         -b21-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaYa EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"مَضَىَ عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went at random, heedlessly, headlong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a heedless,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"headlong, course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiba raA^osahu","text_ar":"رَكِبَ رَاْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rkb","text_ar":"ركب"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b22-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahaba EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"دَهَبَ عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hayovu $aA='a","text_ar":"حَيْثُ شَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away at random whither he would"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swm","text_ar":"سوم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b23-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bal~ato maTiy~atuhu EalaY","text_ar":"بَلَّتْ مَطِيَّتُهُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohihaA","text_ar":"وَجْهِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abal~ato","text_ar":"اَبَلَّتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl","text_ar":"بل"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b24-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uTolubuwA","text_ar":"اُطْلُبُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHawaAy^ija A_inaY HisaAni Alwujuwhi","text_ar":"الحَوَايِجَ اـِنَى حِسَانِ الوُجُوهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make ye petition, for the things that ye want, to persons of good rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"station."},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Hasan El-Muäddib, in TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nDr","text_ar":"نضر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b25-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Consideration and regard."},{"kind":"text","text":"See 3 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Asw","text_ar":"اسو"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b26-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihapN","text_ar":"جِهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The place towards which one goes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Munjid of Kr:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place, region, quarter, part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point, towards which a person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, goes, tends,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is directed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so I have rendered ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihapN","text_ar":"جِهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuqoEN","text_ar":"صُقْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masojuwHN","text_ar":"مَسْجُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihapN","text_ar":"جِهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any place towards which one looks"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wijohupN","text_ar":"وِجْهُةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Har, p. 373:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point, of the tendency"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"direction"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bearing"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: whence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihapa","text_ar":"جِهَةَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the direction of such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijihapK","text_ar":"لِجِهَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards one quarter."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b27-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohu AlT~ariyqi","text_ar":"وَجْهُ الطَّرِيقِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place, to which the way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"road, leads:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*anaAbapN","text_ar":"ذَنَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohu A^amorK","text_ar":"وَجْهُ اَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihatuhu","text_ar":"جِهَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result, of an affair, to which it leads,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tends."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b28-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramawoA wajohFA waAHidFA","text_ar":"رَمَوْا وَجْهًا وَاحِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They shot in one direction"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ri$oqN","text_ar":"رِشْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b29-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohu AlD~uHaY","text_ar":"وَجْهُ الضُّحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning, of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuHaY","text_ar":"ضُحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawonaqN","text_ar":"رَوْنَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) ―         -b30-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A chief"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a people or party. (K.) ―         -b31-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atawoA mano wajohihimo","text_ar":"اَتَوْا مَنْ وَجْهِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faworN","text_ar":"فَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b32-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqapN","text_ar":"طَرِيقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing]. (KL.) ―         -b34-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^adoriY","text_ar":"مَا اَدْرِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA wajohuhu","text_ar":"مَا وَجْهُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I know not what is its meaning."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b35-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a wajohahaA","text_ar":"اَخَذَ وَجْهَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He degraded her; took away her grade:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took her maidenhead:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waj~ahoti sijaAfatahu","text_ar":"وَجَّهْتِ سِجَافَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."}],"source_refs":["K"]}]}}